{"tid":2271332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★螞蟻】滙豐退款安排：將扣除利息和手續費！","createTime":"2020-11-04T13:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T04:35:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":166,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d232d91aa4dbe29fa82733de20ae716695cae8","tid":2271332,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"滙豐發言人表示，該行客戶申請螞蟻集團(06688)上市招股不獲接納部分的款項，將於周三(4日)退回，而原獲得分配股份的款項將於周五(6日)安排退回。客戶如早前申請了新股認購貸款，退款將會扣除截至11月3日的相關利息和手續費<span class=\"xx-large\">(即投資者要付相關金額)</span>，而經數碼渠道遞交申請的客戶早前已獲豁免手續費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201104/bkn-20201104192821275-1104_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201104%2Fbkn-20201104192821275-1104_00842_001.html&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=1bc582d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201104/bkn-20201104192821275-1104_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"03169d204ac9850094c3d655c02533346a8016d7","tid":2271332,"uid":310914,"like":82,"dislike":38,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾銀行始終垃圾銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a0b9cfa84b9a8d09a2adcb0e47f6dd96671557","tid":2271332,"uid":19454,"like":252,"dislike":3,"score":249,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gXXBoC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gXXBoC.gif&h=c77a4b97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"add86bea13d02c572d2051024cb48f51cfdfb9e9","tid":2271332,"uid":19454,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"(即投資者要付相關金額)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><